    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "# Phase B -> Chat + Retrieval Pipeline \n\n## (Telegram → Agent → Pinecone/Web → Telegram)\n\n## Trigger\n- **Telegram Trigger** (On Message Sent)\n\n## Steps\n\n### Main Agent (Gemini 2.5 Pro)\n- Acts as a company HR assistant\n- Follows strict tool policy\n- Memory (context window = 10)\n- Maintains chat continuity per user\n\n### Tools\n1. **Pinecone Vector Store (retrieval)**\n   - Tool name: `documents_tool`\n   - Searches rag-documents\n   - Top K = 5\n2. **Tavily Web Search**\n   - Used ONLY if documents don’t contain the answer\n   - Tool Policy inside Agent:\n     - ALWAYS search documents first\n     - If found → answer only from docs\n     - If not → search web with sources\n     - Never invent company policy\n\n### Additional Processes\n- **Sanitize Telegram Text** (Code Node):\n  - Removes markdown/bullets/escape chars\n  - Makes response Telegram-clean\n- **Send Telegram Message:**\n  - Sends final response to user.\n\n## ✅ Result:\nA grounded RAG chatbot that answers from company docs, with safe web fallback.",
        "height": 1008,
        "width": 1168,
        "color": 7
      },
      "id": "3b2c5d97-4ec1-4231-8619-5b448ef48ef3",
      "name": "Sticky Note2",
