    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "# Phase A -> Smart Document Indexing Pipeline \n\n## Trigger\n\n- Cron (every 2 mins)\n- Polls a specific Google Drive folder continuously\n\n## Steps\n\n1. **Search File in Folder (Google Drive)**\n   - Fetches all files from the target folder with metadata\n\n2. **Loop Over Items**\n   - Processes files one by one\n\n3. **Set (Drive Fields)**\n   - Extracts:\n     - `driveFileId`\n     - `driveFileName`\n     - `driveModified`\n\n4. **Get row(s) in sheet (Google Sheets)**\n   - Checks if this file was indexed before\n   \n   **IF:** `FileId` Empty OR `File Modified`\n   \n   **Logic:**\n   - New file → index\n   - Same file unchanged → skip\n   - Same file modified → re-index\n\n5. **Download file (Google Drive)**\n   - Downloads binary document\n\n6. **Recursive Character Text Splitter**\n   - Chunk overlap: 100\n\n7. **Default Data Loader**\n   - Loads binary into document format\n\n8. **Embeddings Google Gemini (`text-embedding-004`)**\n   - Converts chunks to vectors\n\n9. **Pinecone Vector Store (Inserting)**\n   - Upserts vectors into index: `rag-documents`\n  \n10. **Aggregate**\n    - Waits for all chunks to finish\n    \n11. **Append or Update row in sheet**\n    - Stores:\n      | Field | Description |\n      |---------|--------------|\n      | `fileId` | ID of the file |\n      | `fileName` | Name of the file |\n      | `modifiedTime` | Last modified time |\n      | `indexedAt` | Time of indexing |\n  \ndrive becomes a self-healing vector database with version tracking.",
        "height": 1344,
        "width": 1312,
        "color": 7
      },
      "id": "566333d8-84c2-4229-849a-b4d3608e3268",
      "name": "Sticky Note6",
